<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Unusual Login Attempt - {{appName}}</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        /* Base styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }

        /* Container styles */
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* Alert box */
        .alert-box {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
        }

        /* Login details box */
        .login-details {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        /* Detail row */
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Detail label */
        .detail-label {
            width: 100px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        /* Detail value */
        .detail-value {
            flex: 1;
        }

        /* Button styles */
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ef4444;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Secondary button */
        .button-secondary {
            background-color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* Responsive styles */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100% !important;
            }

            .button {
                width: 100% !important;
                box-sizing: border-box;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .detail-label {
                width: 100%;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    {{> header}}

    <div class="container">
        <h2 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 20px;">⚠️ Unusual Login Attempt</h2>

        <div class="alert-box">
            <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #b91c1c;">Security Alert:</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 8px; color: #b91c1c;">We detected an unusual login attempt to your {{appName}}
                account. This attempt was blocked for your security.</p>
        </div>

        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>

        <p>Our security system has detected an unusual login attempt to your account. To protect your account, we've
            blocked this attempt.</p>

        <div class="login-details">
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Time:</div>
                <div class="detail-value">{{time}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Device:</div>
                <div class="detail-value">{{device}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Location:</div>
                <div class="detail-value">{{location}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Was this you?</strong> If you were trying to log in, you can try again or reset your password.</p>

        <p><strong>Wasn't you?</strong> Your account may be at risk. We strongly recommend taking the following security
            measures immediately:</p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                {{#trackButton resetPasswordUrl "Reset Your Password" emailId "button"}}{{/trackButton}}
            </div>
            <div>
                {{#trackButton (concat appUrl "/account/security") "Review Security Settings" emailId "button
                button-secondary"}}{{/trackButton}}
            </div>
        </div>

        <p>For additional security, consider enabling Two-Factor Authentication on your account if you haven't already.
        </p>

        <p>If you need assistance, please contact our support team immediately.</p>

        <p>Thanks,<br>The {{appName}} Security Team</p>
    </div>

    {{> footer recipient=to emailId=id}}
</body>

</html>